  24 May 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>; -avidemux-9999-r1.ebuild,
  avidemux-9999-r2.ebuild:
  Removing old ebuild. Commented out gcc-4.3 patches as they seem to have been
  applied upstream.

  19 Apr 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>; avidemux-9999-r2.ebuild:
  Adjust qt-4 dep to current portage reality. Setting USE flag defaults.

  13 Apr 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>; avidemux-9999-r2.ebuild:
  Fix encode/lame snafu. This one should work as intended.

  12 Apr 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>;
  +files/avidemux-2.4.1-gcc43-missing-asm-naming.patch,
  +avidemux-9999-r2.ebuild, +files/avidemux-9999-gcc43-includes.patch:
  Bringing ebuild more into sync with in-portage one. Adding gcc-4.3 patches.

  08 Apr 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>; -avidemux-9999.ebuild,
  avidemux-9999-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old version. Adjust x264 dep.

  25 Mar 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>; avidemux-9999-r1.ebuild:
  Changing x264 dep to x264 || x264-svn.

  22 Feb 2008; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>;
  +files/avidemux-2.4-i18n.patch, +avidemux-9999-r1.ebuild:
  Cleaned up the ebuild a bit, adjusting dependancies and configure options to 
  reflect reality :)

  13 Dec 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  +files/avidemux_2.4_branch-libdca.patch, avidemux-9999.ebuild,
  -files/libdca.patch:
  Updated libdca patch.

  01 Dec 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  -avidemux-2.4.0_pre3.ebuild, avidemux-9999.ebuild, +files/libdca.patch:
  Some improvements incorporated from ebuild in portage.
  Removing 2.4.0_pre3 ebuild, as this is now in portage tree.

  26 Nov 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  avidemux-2.4.0_pre3.ebuild, avidemux-9999.ebuild:
  Minor edits in ebuilds.

  17 Nov 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  -avidemux-2.4.0_pre2.ebuild, -avidemux-2.4.0_pre2-r1.ebuild,
  +avidemux-9999.ebuild, -avidemux-24000-r1.ebuild,
  -avidemux-24000-r2.ebuild, -files/dts-internal.patch,
  -files/remove-auto-deps.patch:
  Remove old versions and rename 24000-r2 to 9999.

  12 Nov 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  +avidemux-2.4.0_pre3.ebuild:
  Version bump. We still use libdts as preview3 seems not to want to work with 
  libdca.

  08 Oct 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  +avidemux-24000-r2.ebuild:
  Adding new ebuild, working towards normal useflag behaviour.

  08 Jul 2007; Ben de Groot (yngwin) <ben@berkano.net>;
  +avidemux-2.4.0_pre2-r1.ebuild:
  Adding an alternative ebuild for 2.4_preview2 with the traditional configure 
  routine, in order to comply more closely to Gentoo policies.

  04 Jul 2007; Ben de Groot; +avidemux-2.4.0_pre2.ebuild:
  Adding ebuild for 2.4_preview2.

  21 Jun 2007; Ben de Groot; avidemux-24000-r1.ebuild:
  The cmake based ebuild seems to be working well now, so let's move it to
  "testing". The configuration is still based on autodetect, so disabling
  useflags while having the corresponding dep installed does not work.

  12 Jun 2007; Ben de Groot; avidemux-24000-r1.ebuild:
  Adding dts support to the cmake ebuild, which should now work according to 
  upstream.

  10 Jun 2007; Ben de Groot; +avidemux-24000-r1.ebuild:
  Adding experimental cmake version for 2.4 branch.

  23 May 2007; Ben de Groot; avidemux-24000.ebuild:
  Updating the ebuild so that the qt4 gui builds, removing dts useflag as it
  doesn't build libdca support due to missing dts_internal.h include file.
  Adding debug and extrafilters useflags.

  22 May 2007; Ben de Groot; +avidemux-24000.ebuild:
  Adding 2.4-branch subversion ebuild. Still needs testing.

